Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.50,0:01:14.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,偷吃我秋海棠是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.50,0:01:14.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Biting my begonias, eh?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.55,0:01:16.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有我在就休想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:16.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not on my watch
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.09,0:01:20.26,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1574,940)}邮件
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.59,0:01:19.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,邮递员
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.59,0:01:19.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mailman
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.06,0:01:20.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.06,0:01:20.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wha--?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.50,0:01:29.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.50,0:01:29.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A letter
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.75,0:01:30.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.75,0:01:30.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.86,0:01:36.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(972,406)}诺斯费拉图
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.52,0:01:35.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,诺斯费拉图
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.52,0:01:35.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nosferatu?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.47,0:01:36.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.47,0:01:36.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.82,0:01:40.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又误收到他的邮件了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.82,0:01:40.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got his mail by mistake again
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.82,0:01:46.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就存到这里面好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.82,0:01:46.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll just file that in here
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.15,0:01:53.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.15,0:01:53.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.92,0:01:59.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你躲我垃圾堆里干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.92,0:01:59.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing in my garbage?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.96,0:02:05.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,春季大扫除
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.96,0:02:05.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spring cleaning
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.40,0:02:08.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过章鱼哥  你这样很可耻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.40,0:02:08.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, Squidward, for shame
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.10,0:02:12.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能随便乱丢诺斯费拉图的邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.10,0:02:12.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't just throw out the mail of Nosferatu
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.42,0:02:15.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须亲手送到人家手里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.42,0:02:15.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You have to deliver it yourself
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.95,0:02:19.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然就犯法了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.95,0:02:19.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, it'd be a federal crime
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.60,0:02:22.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也就变成你从犯了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.60,0:02:22.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I'll be an accessory
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.22,0:02:28.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差不多得了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.22,0:02:28.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, already
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.55,0:02:29.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,送就送
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.55,0:02:29.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll take it to him
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.85,0:02:31.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.85,0:02:31.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hurray
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.15,0:02:33.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过邮件得让你带
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.15,0:02:33.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But you are carrying the mail
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.37,0:02:36.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才一封信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.37,0:02:36.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One little letter?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.02,0:02:37.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.02,0:02:37.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No problemo
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.11,0:02:37.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先等下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.11,0:02:37.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.92,0:02:39.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有不少
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.92,0:02:39.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's more
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.43,0:02:42.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些都是他另外的邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.43,0:02:42.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's the rest of it
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.27,0:02:47.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我误收那怪人的邮件已经有好几年了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.27,0:02:44.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have been getting
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.28,0:02:47.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that creepy guy's mail by mistake for years
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.60,0:02:50.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥你看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:50.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, look
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.52,0:02:52.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吸血鬼文摘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.52,0:02:52.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Bleeder's Digest"
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.51,0:02:53.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,精致蝙蝠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.51,0:02:53.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Bat Fancy"
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.92,0:02:55.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,按月订购的鲜血
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.92,0:02:55.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Blood of the Month Club"
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.30,0:03:01.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  知道这代表什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.30,0:03:01.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, do you know what this means?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.41,0:03:03.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.41,0:03:03.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.32,0:03:08.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,代表有人收到邮件就会非常开心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.32,0:03:06.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It means somebody is going to be very happy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.84,0:03:08.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to get all their mail
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.87,0:03:11.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个人就是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.87,0:03:11.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,somebody named
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.08,0:03:13.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,诺斯费拉图
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.08,0:03:13.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nosferatu
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.57,0:03:15.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.57,0:03:15.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.89,0:03:16.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么动静
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.89,0:03:16.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.72,0:03:17.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别盯着我看了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.72,0:03:17.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop looking at me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.93,0:03:26.26,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(914,652)}邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.77,0:03:30.52,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1242,840)}地图
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.12,0:03:30.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里就是收件地址了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.12,0:03:30.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, this is the address
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.46,0:03:37.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,古堡好高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:37.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That castle is so high
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.00,0:03:48.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,算我求你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.00,0:03:48.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, I beg you
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.73,0:03:50.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,千万别去古堡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.73,0:03:50.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,do not go to the castle
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.24,0:03:53.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,堡主是吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.24,0:03:53.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The master is a vampire
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.26,0:03:56.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会吸光你的血
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.26,0:03:56.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He means to suck your blood
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.27,0:04:00.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说的都什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.27,0:04:00.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.16,0:04:05.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,诺斯费拉图
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.16,0:04:05.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nosferatu
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.75,0:04:09.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.75,0:04:09.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.65,0:04:10.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.65,0:04:10.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.59,0:04:12.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我身上没零钱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.59,0:04:12.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't have any spare change
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.52,0:04:13.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,千万别去古堡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:13.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't go to the castle
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.99,0:04:15.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,千万别去古堡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.99,0:04:15.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't go to the castle
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.24,0:04:17.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,千万别去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.24,0:04:17.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't go--
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.00,0:04:31.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去古堡的马车
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.00,0:04:31.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, a coach to the castle
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.30,0:04:33.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太优雅了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.30,0:04:33.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How elegant
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.00,0:04:34.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快走吧  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:34.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Step lively, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.62,0:04:47.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,古堡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.62,0:04:47.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The castle
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.74,0:04:52.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来有人得吃个蟹黄堡了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.74,0:04:52.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like someone could use a Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.95,0:05:34.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回程坐公交车  不坐马车了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.95,0:05:34.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're taking the bus on the way home
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.80,0:06:04.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在吗  诺斯费拉图
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.80,0:06:04.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, Nosferatu?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.85,0:06:08.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来人不在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.85,0:06:08.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, looks like nobody's home
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.13,0:06:11.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.13,0:06:11.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.69,0:06:13.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.69,0:06:13.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.15,0:06:20.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们是来这送你邮件的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.15,0:06:20.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're just here to drop off your mail
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.32,0:06:26.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:26.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.95,0:06:32.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来是诺斯费拉图
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.95,0:06:32.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's just Nosferatu
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.42,0:06:51.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,主人向你们表示欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.42,0:06:51.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The master bids you welcome
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.80,0:06:55.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,并且感谢你们来送邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:55.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and he thanks you for dropping off his mail
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.27,0:07:29.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.27,0:07:29.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Knock it off
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.40,0:07:32.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.40,0:07:32.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am sorry, Master
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.90,0:07:34.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以后不会再犯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.90,0:07:34.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It won't happen again
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.12,0:07:42.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们这就走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.12,0:07:42.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll let ourselves out
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.33,0:07:44.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还不想走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.33,0:07:44.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't want to leave
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.89,0:07:53.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天气太恶劣  你们现在走不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.89,0:07:53.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't leave due to inclement weather
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.22,0:07:54.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们走不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.22,0:07:54.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can't leave yet
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.27,0:08:00.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咽口水
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.27,0:08:00.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gulp
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.00,0:08:03.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,主人邀请你们在这过夜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:03.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Master has invited you to stay for the night
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.62,0:08:07.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过他想先与你们共进晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.62,0:08:07.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but first, he would like to have you both for dinner
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.50,0:08:14.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.50,0:08:14.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.50,0:08:16.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在这种情况吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.50,0:08:16.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,under the circumstances
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.10,0:08:19.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不介意来点特兰西瓦尼亚美食
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:19.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind some fine Transylvanian cuisine
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:19.55,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 特兰西瓦尼亚：传说中的吸血鬼故乡 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.55,0:08:20.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,换换口味
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.55,0:08:20.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for a change
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:20.77,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1026,924)}零 钱
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.27,0:08:22.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,零钱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.27,0:08:22.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Change?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.25,0:08:23.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以换零钱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.25,0:08:23.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can make change
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.94,0:08:26.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我走开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.94,0:08:26.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get away from me
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.02,0:08:30.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来  来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.02,0:08:30.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come, come
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.63,0:08:50.21,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1568,276)}精致蝙蝠
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.90,0:08:53.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好丰盛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.90,0:08:53.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a spread
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.32,0:08:55.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道要先尝哪个了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.32,0:08:55.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to try first
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.07,0:08:58.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来帮你挑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.07,0:08:58.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can help you decide
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.47,0:09:03.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们有烤狼人牙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.47,0:09:03.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We have roasted werewolf teeth
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.00,0:09:05.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,腌恶魔胡须
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.00,0:09:05.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,pickled demon beards
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.08,0:09:08.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,炸木乃伊手指
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.08,0:09:08.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,fried mummy fingers
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.23,0:09:10.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有鞑靼大脑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.23,0:09:10.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and brains tartare
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.85,0:09:13.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就不客气开吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.85,0:09:13.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't mind if I do--
Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.15,0:09:19.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许你们想要点邪恶多汁佳肴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.15,0:09:19.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or maybe you would like something sinfully succulent
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.59,0:09:23.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喀尔巴阡起司球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.59,0:09:23.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A Carpathian cheese ball
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.59,0:09:23.30,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 特兰西瓦尼亚位于东喀尔巴阡山以西 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.81,0:09:27.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是我的饭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.81,0:09:27.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's my dinner
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.53,0:09:28.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快来爸爸这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.53,0:09:28.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come to daddy
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.62,0:09:35.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定得来尝尝木乃伊手指  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.62,0:09:35.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've got to try these mummy fingers, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.55,0:09:37.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.55,0:09:37.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So delicious
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.30,0:09:39.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,诺斯费拉图  务必给我一份秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:39.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nosferatu, you simply must give me the recipe
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.93,0:09:46.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还是加点番茄酱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.93,0:09:46.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe if I put some ketchup on it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.44,0:09:48.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,番茄酱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:48.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ketchup?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.22,0:09:49.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,幸好我有备而来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.22,0:09:49.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good thing I came prepared
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.61,0:09:52.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开加番茄酱了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.61,0:09:52.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ketching up
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.92,0:10:12.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,诺斯费拉图  来点番茄酱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.92,0:10:12.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nosferatu, ketchup?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.28,0:10:23.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,主人说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.28,0:10:23.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Master says
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.05,0:10:27.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,睡个安稳觉  别让吸血鬼蝙蝠咬了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.05,0:10:27.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Sleep tight and don't let the vampire bats bite"
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.55,0:10:39.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,主人向你们表示晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.55,0:10:39.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Master bids you good night
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.36,0:10:44.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安  诺斯费拉图
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.36,0:10:44.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good night, Nosferatu
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.60,0:10:51.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这地方让我毛毛的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.60,0:10:51.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This place gives me the creeps
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.92,0:10:53.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,倒也没啥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:53.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But so what?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.04,0:10:54.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才住一夜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.04,0:10:54.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's only one night
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.56,0:10:55.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对吧  海绵宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.56,0:10:55.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right, SpongeB--
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.31,0:11:03.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,忘刷牙了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.31,0:11:03.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forgot to brush my teeth
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.42,0:11:13.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,忘用牙线剔牙了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.42,0:11:13.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forgot to floss
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.83,0:11:21.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,忘洗头了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.83,0:11:21.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forgot to wash my head
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.23,0:11:27.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,忘擦亮眼睛了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.23,0:11:27.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forgot to polish my eyes
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.47,0:11:33.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能给我好好睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.47,0:11:33.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will you go night night time already?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.02,0:11:34.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,诺斯费拉图
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.02,0:11:34.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nosferatu?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.32,0:11:37.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你干嘛要从墙里那样探出头来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.32,0:11:37.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why are you sticking out of the wall like that?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:43.15,0:11:45.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,诺斯费拉图居然要咬我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.15,0:11:45.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe Nosferatu tried to bite me
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.87,0:11:49.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他是活生生的吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.87,0:11:49.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's a real life v-v-vampire
Dialogue: 1,0:11:49.15,0:11:51.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他要吸光我们的血
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.15,0:11:51.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's gonna suck our blood
Dialogue: 1,0:11:53.11,0:11:56.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定有办法可以逃出古堡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.11,0:11:56.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's got to be a way out of this castle
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.35,0:11:59.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来带你们出去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.35,0:11:59.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can show you a way out
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.00,0:12:07.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,史赖皮好困
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.00,0:12:07.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Slappy sleepy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.48,0:12:10.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走这几扇门试试
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.48,0:12:10.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's try these doors
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.87,0:12:24.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,猩猩怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.87,0:12:24.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gorilla monster
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.90,0:12:28.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快  走洗衣滑槽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.90,0:12:28.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quick, down the laundry chute
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.82,0:12:43.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吸血鬼棺材
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.82,0:12:43.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a vampire's coffin
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.76,0:12:55.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,诺斯费拉图两步舞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.76,0:12:55.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nosferatu two-step
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.52,0:13:03.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赶紧回神  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.52,0:13:03.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Snap out of it, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.20,0:13:04.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万一他咬了我们脖子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.20,0:13:04.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What if he bites our necks
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.66,0:13:07.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或者我鼻子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:07.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or my nose?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.92,0:13:09.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.92,0:13:09.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know what to do
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.12,0:13:12.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吸血鬼电影主角都会做木桩打吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.12,0:13:10.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In those vampire movies
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.57,0:13:12.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,they always make wooden stakes
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.42,0:13:14.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是好办法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.42,0:13:14.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a great idea
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.95,0:13:15.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.95,0:13:15.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.73,0:13:20.65,注释,,0,0,0,,[ stake（木桩）与 steak（牛排）谐音 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.02,0:13:20.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没牛排酱还会有效吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.02,0:13:20.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will these even work without steak sauce?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.34,0:13:30.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们不应该来缠扰主人的衣坟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.34,0:13:30.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't disturb the master's laundry tomb
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.80,0:13:34.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他发现你们来这  一定会发火的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.80,0:13:34.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He would be very cranky if he found you here
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.92,0:13:38.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且你们永远不知道他身处何方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.92,0:13:38.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and you never know where he might be
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.06,0:13:40.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他是不是就在我们身后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.06,0:13:40.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's right behind us, isn't he?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.92,0:13:42.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:42.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.50,0:13:43.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,后面没人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.50,0:13:43.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nobody there
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.30,0:13:44.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:44.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're fine
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.72,0:13:49.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你别吃我们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.72,0:13:49.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please don't eat us
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.71,0:13:52.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,主人不饿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.71,0:13:52.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The master is not hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.90,0:13:55.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他刚刚吃了一顿大餐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.90,0:13:55.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He just had a big lunch
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.14,0:13:57.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他想把你们的邮件还回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.14,0:13:57.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He wanted to return your mail
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.52,0:14:01.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可真贴心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.52,0:14:01.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, how thoughtful of you
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.43,0:14:03.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.43,0:14:03.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.97,0:14:05.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打开看看  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.97,0:14:05.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Open it, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.27,0:14:06.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.27,0:14:06.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What'd you get?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.07,0:14:06.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:06.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.96,0:14:08.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.96,0:14:08.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.07,0:14:10.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我按月订购的大蒜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:10.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's my Garlic of the Month Club
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.23,0:14:11.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.23,0:14:11.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.64,0:14:21.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,主人只是在耍你们而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.64,0:14:21.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The master is just joshing with you
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.47,0:14:23.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他可喜欢大蒜了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.47,0:14:23.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He loves garlic
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.01,0:14:34.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果把灯弄得闪来闪去的不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.01,0:14:34.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, if you're not flicking the lights on and off
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.00,0:14:35.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会是谁在搞鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.00,0:14:35.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,then who is?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.80,0:14:41.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,歌剧魅影
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.80,0:14:41.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Phantom of the Opera
