Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.84,0:15:24.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pick me
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.57,0:15:24.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.57,0:15:24.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.98,0:15:25.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,选我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.98,0:15:25.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pick me
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.60,0:15:26.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,选
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.60,0:15:26.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pick--
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.18,0:15:27.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,选我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.18,0:15:27.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,pick me
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.01,0:15:27.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.01,0:15:27.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.13,0:15:44.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,埃斯梅拉达
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.13,0:15:44.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Esmeralda
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.52,0:15:46.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.52,0:15:46.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good evening
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.69,0:16:08.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快醒醒  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.69,0:16:08.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wakey-wakes, Master
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.62,0:16:12.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一日之计在于每天吸到的第一滴血
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.62,0:16:12.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The first blood of the day is the most important
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.07,0:16:15.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.07,0:16:15.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Master?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.19,0:16:23.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.19,0:16:23.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.58,0:16:26.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你鼻子肿得费拉图不堪了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.58,0:16:26.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've got a stuffy Nose-feratu
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.14,0:16:38.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须带你去找鱿医生治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.14,0:16:38.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We have to get you to Dr. Calamari right away
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:17:01.08,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1130,214)}鱿医生
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.26,0:17:02.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一位病人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.26,0:17:02.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next patient
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.17,0:17:06.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  鱿医生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.17,0:17:06.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Salutations, Dr. Calamari
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.55,0:17:10.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,主人得了特兰西瓦尼亚吸吸症
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.55,0:17:07.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The master has a case of
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.98,0:17:10.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the Transylvanian sniff-sniffs
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.79,0:17:12.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以治好他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.79,0:17:12.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can you help?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.53,0:17:15.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢你带你主人过来  史赖皮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.53,0:17:15.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you for bringing him in, Slappy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.82,0:17:19.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会把过敏原蒸出他鼻子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.82,0:17:19.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll steam those allergies right out of his schnoz
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.47,0:17:28.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两小时后回来接他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.47,0:17:28.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come back in two hours und pick him up
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.88,0:17:30.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我马上回来  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.88,0:17:30.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll be right back, Master
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.37,0:17:32.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差点忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.37,0:17:32.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I almost forgot
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.02,0:17:47.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是的  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.02,0:17:47.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Master
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.90,0:17:52.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会带来血样与饼干的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.90,0:17:52.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I will bring you blood samples und cookies
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.97,0:17:54.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两小时
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.97,0:17:54.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Two hours?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.65,0:17:57.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两小时要来干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.65,0:17:57.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What am I gonna do for two whole hours?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.00,0:18:00.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来随便做做看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.00,0:18:00.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's find out, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:04.56,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1570,216)}裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:05.81,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(956,384)}欢乐游戏厅\N全场游戏两毛五
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:15.90,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1176,410)}坟头蹦迪
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.21,0:18:12.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起来坟头蹦迪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.21,0:18:12.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get ready to prance, prance on your grave
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.44,0:18:15.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱蹦迪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.44,0:18:15.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just love to prance
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.05,0:18:20.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉真是自由奔放
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.05,0:18:20.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I feel so free and loose
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.31,0:18:34.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.31,0:18:34.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.39,0:18:36.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,空心球进了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.39,0:18:36.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I made a swish
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.22,0:18:43.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快来喷水赢大奖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.22,0:18:43.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Step right up and squirt yourself a prize
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.51,0:18:41.64,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1012,324)}水管喷水瓶
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.35,0:18:45.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.35,0:18:45.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.83,0:18:48.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赢家出炉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.83,0:18:48.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We have a winner
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.47,0:18:49.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赢家  赢家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.47,0:18:49.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Winner, winner
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.30,0:18:53.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快来喷水赢大奖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.30,0:18:53.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Step right up and squirt yourself a prize
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.68,0:18:56.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,升天去吧  瓶子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.68,0:18:56.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Reach for the sky, bottles
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.03,0:18:59.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快来喷水
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.03,0:18:59.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Step right up, and squ--
Dialogue: 1,0:19:06.82,0:19:09.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又有赢家出炉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.82,0:19:09.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We have another winner
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.34,0:19:22.39,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(938,238)}宠物店
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.14,0:19:24.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  史莉皮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.14,0:19:24.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, Slippy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.55,0:19:28.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你今晚样子可真是恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.55,0:19:28.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You look positively disgusting this evening
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.17,0:19:36.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你自己样子也挺难看  史赖皮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.17,0:19:36.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You look pretty horrifying yourself, Slappy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.60,0:19:46.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想买什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.60,0:19:46.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What can I get you today?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.63,0:19:51.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要给主人买罐蝙蝠粮和跳蚤项圈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.63,0:19:51.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need a can of bat food and a flea collar for the master
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.05,0:19:57.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你主人有你的照顾  运气可真是好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.05,0:19:54.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That master sure is lucky
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.77,0:19:57.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to have you looking out for him
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.65,0:20:02.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一共多少钱  母夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.65,0:20:02.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do I owe you, gruesome?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.72,0:20:07.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用钱  臭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.72,0:20:07.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's on the house, stink lips
Dialogue: 1,0:20:09.47,0:20:13.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们以后再见吧  亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.47,0:20:13.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Until our eyes cross again, mon cheri
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.30,0:20:23.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.30,0:20:23.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.37,0:20:25.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这边有蜗牛尿布卖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.37,0:20:25.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you sell snail diapers?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.18,0:20:33.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,与旧日好友一同野餐  感觉就是好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.18,0:20:33.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is always great to go on a picnic with old friends
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.75,0:20:36.50,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1358,204)}墓地
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.20,0:20:36.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,排骨眼先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.20,0:20:36.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mr. Ribeye?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.50,0:20:39.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,排骨眼先生  现在几点了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.50,0:20:39.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ribeye, do you have the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.50,0:20:44.84,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(518,254)}排骨眼先生\N{\fnArial}1117{\fnAdobe 黑体 Std R}年生 {\fnArial}1198{\fnAdobe 黑体 Std R}年卒
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.67,0:20:43.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得去接主人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.67,0:20:43.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have to pick up the master
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.84,0:20:46.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家再见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:46.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you soon, everyone
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.77,0:20:49.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过别太快就见了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.77,0:20:49.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but hopefully not too soon
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.67,0:20:53.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.67,0:20:53.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bye
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.19,0:20:54.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,改天再见  史赖皮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.19,0:20:54.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you later, Slappy
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.15,0:20:54.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.15,0:20:54.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.70,0:20:55.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以后再来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.70,0:20:55.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come back soon
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.69,0:21:01.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,诺斯费拉图
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.69,0:21:01.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nosferatu
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.32,0:21:04.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鱿医生  我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.32,0:21:04.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dr. Calamari, I'm back
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.99,0:21:09.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,诺斯费拉图
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.99,0:21:09.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nosferatu
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.12,0:21:10.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说吧  医生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.12,0:21:10.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So tell me, Doctor
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.70,0:21:12.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,主人治好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.70,0:21:12.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is the master cured?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.80,0:21:14.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已经康复了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.80,0:21:14.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All better
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.15,0:21:17.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每天晚上滴两次滴鼻液
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.15,0:21:17.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make sure he takes these nose drops twice a night
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.39,0:21:20.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢  鱿医生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.39,0:21:20.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Dr. C
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.18,0:21:23.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁是乖吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.18,0:21:23.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who was a good vampire?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.41,0:21:41.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是的  我当然给你买了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.41,0:21:41.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, of course I bought you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.90,0:21:44.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你先前在橱窗那边看到过的跳蚤项圈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.90,0:21:44.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that flea collar you saw in the window
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.70,0:21:48.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帅气迷人啊  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:48.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Very fetching, Master
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.97,0:21:55.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,存进冰箱里等会儿吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.97,0:21:55.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll put that in the fridge for later
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.64,0:22:00.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用谢我  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.64,0:22:00.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't have to thank me, Master
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.75,0:22:03.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是我最好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.75,0:22:03.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're my best friend
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.25,0:22:08.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是的  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.25,0:22:08.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Master
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.01,0:22:10.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.01,0:22:10.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go home now
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.53,0:22:17.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第一个进古堡的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.53,0:22:17.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,First one to the castle
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.14,0:22:21.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,变又脏又臭绝望大粪坑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.14,0:22:21.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is a filthy, stinking cesspool of despair
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.04,0:22:33.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我像蝙蝠一样遨游天际
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.04,0:22:33.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am soaring like a bat
Dialogue: 1,0:22:33.72,0:22:35.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遨游天际
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.72,0:22:35.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Soaring
